1578551567--select  if(ifnull(c.sort_name_sku,'')='',d.sort_name,c.sort_name_sku) as sort_name,a.title as otitle,d.title,a.outer_id,a.outer_sku_id,c.prd_sku_id,a.market,a.floor,a.booth,a.prd_no,a.sku_name,count(1) num, ifnull(NULLIF(b.price,0),ifnull(NULLIF(c.cost_price,0),d.cost_price)) as price, ifnull(NULLIF(d.cus_no,''), SUBSTRING_INDEX(a.prd_no,'-',3)) as cus_no, a.pic_url ,e.name as prd_loc
		from u13123456789_tid_items a
			left join (
				SELECT prd_no,price FROM (
					SELECT * FROM u13123456789_prdt_up ORDER BY begin_datetime DESC
				) AS a GROUP BY a.prd_no
			) as b on b.prd_no=a.prd_no
			left join (
				select prd_sku_id,prd_sku_no,cost_price,sort_name_sku from u13123456789_product_sku WHERE prd_sku_no<>'' group by prd_sku_no
			) as c on c.prd_sku_no=a.outer_sku_id
			left join (
				select prd_id,cost_price,sort_name,cus_no,title from u13123456789_product group by prd_id
			) as d on d.prd_id=a.prd_id
			left join (
				select prd_loc,name from u13123456789_wh_loc ORDER BY id
			) as e on a.prd_loc = e.prd_loc 
			inner join (select tid,fetch_detail from u13123456789_tid_orders where send_status in ('WAIT_ASSIGN','WAIT_FINISH_ASSIGN') and mark_status<>'LOCK') as statussql on a.tid=statussql.tid  where a.tid in ('XX-15752760032640','XX-15752764344939','XX-15752767824536','XX-15752768295516_1','XX-15752768734765','TB-15762174617762','TB-15767325281720','TB-15776971815682','TB-15777736586547','TB-15777837278382','TB-15785507148161') and refund_status != 'SUCCESS' and close_unique_code=0 and a.check_stock='0'
			group by ifnull(NULLIF(d.cus_no,''), SUBSTRING_INDEX(a.prd_no,'-',3)), a.market,a.floor,a.booth,if(ifnull(d.sort_name,'')='',a.prd_no,d.sort_name),a.sku_name order by statussql.fetch_detail,ifnull(NULLIF(d.cus_no,''), SUBSTRING_INDEX(a.prd_no,'-',3)), a.market,a.floor,if(ifnull(d.sort_name,'')='',a.prd_no,d.sort_name)

1578557259--SELECT b.title,b.pic_url,b.sku_name,b.prd_no,a.express_type,COUNT(1) AS tid_num,SUM(a.items_num) AS items_num,b.market,b.floor,b.booth,b.prd_id,b.prd_sku_id FROM u13123456789_tid_items b 
				INNER JOIN (SELECT new_tid,tid,items_num,express_type FROM u13123456789_tid_orders a  where a.send_status in ('WAIT_ASSIGN','WAIT_FINISH_ASSIGN','WAIT_SENDED_ASSIGN') AND a.exception_online=0 AND a.sku_num=1 AND a.stock_order=0   AND a.mark_status <> 'LOCK' AND items_num=1 ) AS a ON a.tid=b.tid
				
				WHERE  b.close_unique_code = 0 AND  refund_status <> 'SUCCESS'  AND refund_status <> 'WAIT_SELLER_AGREE' 
				GROUP BY b.prd_no,b.sku_name,a.express_type order by b.prd_no DESC limit 0,50
